OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain in
OL,6,Fthe east towards Inverness and Great
OL,7,FGlen will soon clear. Otherwise mainly
OL,8,Fdry with bright or sunny spells but a
OL,9,Ffew showers will spread into the
OL,10,Fwest.Fresh southwest winds across the
OL,11,FHebrides.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy evening with
OL,14,Fsome showery rain moving eastwards.
OL,15,FThen mainly dry with clear spells but
OL,16,Fa few showers continuing in the far
OL,17,Fnorth. Patchy frost and ice possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
