OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA frost to start the day in
OL,6,Fsome places. A dry day with good
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine but some high cloud
OL,8,Fwill spread across at times.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,11,Fdry and bright on Wednesday but
OL,12,Fcloudier with outbreaks of rain later.
OL,13,FRain bands moving east followed by
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter spells for the rest
OL,15,Fof the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
